Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.30,0:00:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.80,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本是高中生工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被灌下毒藥而身體變小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體雖然變小頭腦還是一樣的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有迷宮的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的事件是延續上集的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同學會殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.10,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著緊張的心跳聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華麗的解決事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.40,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在溫泉旅館"弁慶"裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔跟他的大學同學在這裡舉辦柔道社的同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參加的人有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社團經理 崛越由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在在經營模型生意的 大村淳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔任高中體育老師的 綾城行雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及他的太太 紀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現任千葉警局的員警 中道和志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後就是叔叔、蘭跟我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.20,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在煙火大會結束之後回到旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一時興起想一起把由美叫醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現的卻是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨舉槍自盡後的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過鑑識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現由美死亡的時間是在七個小時以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是大家出發看煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起在打桌球的 下午三點鐘左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小五郎同學會殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來我想起由美說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想 我還真的是不想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 她早就想不開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨是怎麼射自己頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要問些奇怪的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還需要問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.30,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她當然是這樣子拿著槍抵著頭部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般舉槍自殺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍口應該都會和頭部密合對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美的傷口上卻沒有應該有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會有燒傷的痕跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為開槍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子彈會和一股高溫的熱風一起從槍口噴出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果槍口抵著頭部的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭上應該會有燒傷的痕跡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有燒傷的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就表示是別人開槍射殺由美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他故意讓由美看起來像自殺的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個殺人的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這間旅館裡的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們懷疑這件事情是我們兩個人幹的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別瞎猜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們剛才也說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美是下午三點左右遇害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是和我們分開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們從三點到六點之間都一直在桌球室打桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是不可能行兇的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一段期間內唯一離開桌球場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有去上廁所的阿淳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得那個時候好像是五點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他不到一分鐘就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以阿淳也不可能行兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說難道是外部的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照屋簷的設計來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手可以從屋簷通到任何地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且入口的門也沒有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以外面的人的確很有可能進到裡面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之 我們先問問旅館的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許他們有看到什麼可疑的人物也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.20,0:04:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概下午三點鐘左右的陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候是午休 我們正好都出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我們再回到旅館以後也沒看到什麼可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來有個人的確很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個帶著孩子的年輕女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的樣子匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來以後二話不說就直衝二樓去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女人有什麼特徵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不就站在你們後頭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得那個時候正好是六點半開始放煙火的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是因為煙火開放了才跑回來叫由美阿姨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後我們就走到由美阿姨的房間前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來打算到她房裡去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我阻止了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為由美最討厭被人吵醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼你那個時候還留在旅館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為打桌球出了一身汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就先到大浴堂去洗了一個澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我想帶著滿身汗臭去看煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你和阿淳都不太好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候你們兩個好像也去洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們兩個是到露天浴池去洗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們硬把由美叫起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定由美就不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美她是在我們打桌球的時候就已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算叫她的話那也不可能來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔我有一件事情想要請問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿淳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底隱瞞了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從傍晚開始就一直不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底隱瞞了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 我哪有隱瞞什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不小心看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我從桌球室去廁所的時候看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看見兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去上廁所的時候都已經五點多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美在那個時候早就已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那個時候就是看到已經死了的由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到她從二樓的視窗表情嚴肅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直瞪著桌球場的一舉一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那時候會看見由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能有這種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.70,0:07:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到的那個由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說傻話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世界上根本沒什麼鬼魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你是因為太累弄得腦袋不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會以為看到那種東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.60,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 我們弁慶旅館到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們剛才在說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有一個朋友在房裡被人用槍射殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那得快點替她包紮才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方這時候已經朝這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人當時為什麼會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道那個殺人的兇手就是你們之中的一人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這當然不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手是我們之外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您不需要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志 接下來的交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去廁所方便一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就認定是外部犯做的還太早了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為由美阿姨被殺的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有在聽我說話 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用不著你這小鬼說三道四的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼叫另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是從外面進入的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何必要讓她偽裝成自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手根本就是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手就是我的死黨之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是為了什麼用什麼方法殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.10,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這一次我絕不會饒了那個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著瞧吧 我一定要把他揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手就是他們四人當中的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經確定犯人的範圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許就是那個時候說溜了嘴的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那個人有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那個時候大家都在桌球場打桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也調查過由美阿姨死亡的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒有錯才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨當時手上雖然拿著那把手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是她的手指根本沒有扣到板機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要她看起來像自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手指就應該放在板機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且由美阿姨當時並沒有穿內衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身上也被換了大好幾號的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是兇手幫她換的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弁慶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 這家旅館的名字就叫做弁慶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他身上之所以會有這麼多箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為弁慶死的時候是站著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站著死的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 是弁慶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手利用的就是這個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人使用的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.70,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 就用這個手錶麻醉槍像以前一樣讓叔叔睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手根本就是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手就是這些死黨之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這一次我絕不會饒了那個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著瞧吧 我一定要把他揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是算了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手到底為什麼要殺由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是跑進來偷東西的時候剛好被由美撞見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 這也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有 我們打桌球的時候為什麼都沒聽到槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個兇手明明就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼都有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美死亡的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從她死後僵硬的程度來看是下午三點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說由美被殺是在和我們分開之後回到房間以後的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.90,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在三點到六點多鐘之間都在桌球場打球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都沒有機會殺她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是阿淳說的那句話有點不太尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那個時候就是看到已經死了的由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到她從二樓的視窗表情嚴肅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直瞪著桌球場的一舉一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿淳去上廁所大概是五點過後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美不可能活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿淳為什麼要這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來打桌球 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都這個時候了 你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的握手式打法也很厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 由美阿姨也是握手式打法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭姐姐妳不是也看過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一張照片上面正好就照到她橫握著球拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之還是不行 現在不能打桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是流汗的話 又得換一件衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手式打法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在聯想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美的確是被換了件大號的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且身上還沒有穿內衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連握手槍的右手和食指部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也都沒有扣到板機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是直直的伸在槍身外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手式打法正好就是將食指伸直握著球拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美在她被殺以前曾經和兇手打過桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手幹嘛要這麼大費周章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前在警察學校的時候我記得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弁慶死的時候是不是一直直直的站著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為弁慶憑著一個人卻必須要對抗無數的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會身中很多箭之後站著死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 就是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫這麼大聲到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子我終於知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺由美的兇手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺由美的兇手就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺由美的兇手就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 和志殺了由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們推斷由美的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我明明就跟你們在桌球場打球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你有很完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過前提必須是由美真正死於下午三點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.30,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美死後的驗屍明明就是我跟你兩個人一起做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.30,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候由美的屍體的確連腳趾都開始僵硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才會認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美的死亡時間一定超過七個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是還有例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是在激烈的運動途中發生的猝死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人體肌肉內的蛋白質很容易快速凝固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以死後僵硬的情況也會比一般人要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就和一世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏弁慶死的時候是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那弁慶會站著死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以站著斷氣也是有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這在醫學上已經得到了證實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是陳屍的地點可是由美自己的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你倒說說看 我能夠在那裏讓由美做什麼運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.10,0:15:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美死前並不是在她自己的房間裡運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是桌球場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在由美死亡前的這段時間你都跟她在打桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.40,0:15:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也許你早就和由美約好在桌球場見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你在那之前才會建議大家一起到桌球場去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.10,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們待會兒一塊兒去打桌球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說去就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美當然會生氣的回自己房裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等六點之後我們全都離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美才一個人來到你早就等在那裡的桌球場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你們一定有什麼秘密要談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以由美才會答應你約她打球的邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運動一段時間之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在由美回到自己房間的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就在由美的房裡用預藏的手槍殺了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之所以將死亡時間大幅度的提前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是為了製造你的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要安排由美回自己房間很容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為由美是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要利用她的性格就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是由美手上還拿著球拍就慌慌張張的回房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會讓她右手拿著手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為她的右手已經因為握球拍快速僵硬的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我五點多看到的那個由美是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那的確是由美本人沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實那個時候她還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她會從二樓往桌球場看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要等只剩和志一個人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美被殺身亡的真正時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是六點半煙火開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他配合著煙火 就算有槍聲也不容易被發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志這個時候還有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他必須把屍體的汗擦掉然後換一件浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為如果發現她大量流汗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個手法很容易就被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候他只有把由美的浴衣脫下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換上他早就準備好的一件新浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候突然有人跑來礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭和柯南正好回來想要叫醒由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的後置工作還沒有做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就先從窗戶爬到屋簷來到走廊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適時阻止了蘭進房裡的企圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後你趁著大家一起去煙火會場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假藉被人群擠散的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又回來把剩下的工作完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓由美手上握著手槍讓人以為她是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.40,0:17:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時由美的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為打桌球的關係早就僵硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以食指根本就沒有辦法扣板機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這番推理的確很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你有什麼證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑什麼說一定是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用狡辯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡會用那種手法的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我跟你這個當警察的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你也有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這種普通常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要仔細的到書裡找找 誰都會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好笨哦 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼厲害的警察怎麼可能是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這個警察光是看到滿身是血的由美阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就知道她已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得你那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確叫大家不要亂碰由美的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要碰她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這個房間裡面除了我這個警察和毛利這個偵探之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不可以進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.90,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓蘭叫的不是救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你早就已經知道已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為由美就是被你殺的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好小子 你竟然殺了由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我本來也不想殺她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼說我跟由美都交往了十八年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我相親的半年前我們都還有來往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你是怕她妨礙你結婚所以才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼不跟由美結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾經向她求過好幾次婚但都被否決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八年來一直如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在無計可施的情況下終於決定和相親的對象結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是由美卻對我這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會讓你一個人幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那個時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美對我的未婚妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是寄恐嚇信就是打恐嚇電話騷擾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且鬧到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她還威脅要把我們兩個人的照片寄給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我只好說相片我買下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫她把相片全部帶到同學會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實就是那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你抓到搶匪的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我剛好和由美正要分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我正在煩惱該拿由美這種脾氣怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀行搶匪的那把槍就滾到我的眼前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.50,0:20:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就在那個時候想到了這次的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們約好了在桌球場交照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候我就這麼對她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把照片從妳的袋子裡拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以由美才會慌張的回房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手上還握著球拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後你追到房門的時候才把她給殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的人生全都被她給毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是個惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底誰才是惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本什麼都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有權利說我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種想殺人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想去懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是老樣子 功力一點也沒退步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.30,0:21:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你自己的心跟身體都已經老化退步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔最近好像沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.60,0:23:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也沒辦法接受老朋友做了那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 既然叔叔這麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼比賽都沒有贏過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.80,0:23:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說爸爸一到比賽的時候就會特別的緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.50,0:23:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全都用在不對的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.60,0:23:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他也會怕比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我去讓他打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.70,0:23:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看還是暫時讓他靜一靜好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他馬上就會恢復的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.70,0:23:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是粉紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然目前還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.80,0:24:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真是照她所說 這隻狗真會襲擊人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們恐怕只好讓牠安樂死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.90,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.10,0:24:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠救約翰的就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.50,0:24:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.00,0:24:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛犬約翰殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.30,0:24:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.50,0:24:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,條件反射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.00,0:24:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一回是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約翰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.70,0:24:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.30,0:24:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 吃吧
